title: Premium Spin Cycle™ Mop with Bucket
description:
The washing machine for your mop! This mop features:
•Built in washing spinner in the bottom of bucket
•One spinner for washing, one spinner for drying
•Durable stainless steel wringer basket
•Push down handle for spinning & wringing
•Built in and removable easy to fill soap pump
•Sliding handle and wheels on bottom of bucket for easy moving from one room to the next (no heavy lifting)
•Built in drawer for sponge/refill/brush storage
